2. Why PMP0 cannot schedule

Your pmp0 pod requests:

CPU request: 5

CPU limit: 9


The scheduler says:

0/1 nodes are available: 1 Insufficient cpu

The node currently has:

CPU requests: 103862m (≈103.9 CPUs)

